fields.description:
Hi,
I just build an application on titanium studio which got executed successfully, the I changed my system date to 3 days ahead and then back to my current date. Now it is not building my application.

Titanium Studio 3.2.0
Mobile SDK 3.2.0
Alloy 1.3.0
